Just a few quick notes with my books opening. Please keep in mind I do all my own bookings and admin work so opening my books is a relatively stressful time so please be kind. Answering all the requests usually takes me two to three weeks.

My books are now open for the fall! (Oct 2023 to the end of December 2023)! The link to my tattoo application form is at the top of my page. 
I would adore to take on some large scale work but I am also very open to small pieces too. 
I do coverup work of scars and also of old tattoos depending upon what you have and what you would like to cover it with so please include photos of the area you are wanting to get tattooed. 

Some random things I would love to tattoo are, big floral designs, large leafy plant projects, cute animals, bottles, crystals/gems. skulls and mushrooms always, sweet treats!!!! Ice cream cookies and candies, most things pop culture related, I would love to tattoo more food designs in general. These are just some ideas the possibilities are endless.

 I typically tattoo 4 to 5 people a week (big pieces also take multiple sittings) so I have very limited space available. Due to the large number of requests I get I won’t be able to take on every project. Please do not be offended if I say no, it is not personal at all. I hate letting people down but I am trying my best to set boundaries that will keep me happy and healthy and not over worked. 

Thanks for all the love and support I look forward to reading everyone’s submissions 🖤
.
